From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Apr 2026 08:14:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Reorganize repo: split theta_optimizer monolith, move BFS
 scheduler, trim re-exports

- Split 1288-line theta_optimizer.py into 5 focused modules (types, linear_solvers,
  implicit_grad, wave_optimizer, genewise_optimizer) with backward-compatible facade
